metadata.description: It's back, the complete reprint of Gold Key's Time Tunnel comic book series. This is the second volume of Hermes Press's complete reprints of all of the Irwin Allen sci-fi television show tie-in comics. Now, read both issues, back-to-back, together with documentary material, essays, blue prints from the show and more! Full color and digitally remastered, The Time Tunnel: The Complete Series brings these comic books back looking better than when they first hit the stands.
metadata.name: The Time Tunnel: The Complete Series
